   Welcome to the FPPC Web Site What's New at FPPC?
   The Mission of the FAIR POLITICAL PRACTICES COMMISSION is to promote
   the integrity of representative state and local government in
   California through fair, impartial interpretation and enforcement of
   political campaign, lobbying, and conflict of interest laws.


                          FPPC's Toll-Free Number:
                               1-866-ASK-FPPC
                              (1-866-275-3772)
                               Privacy Policy
                            The FPPC is hiring.


                              Register to Vote
   February 19, 2002, is the last day to register to vote in the March 5,
      2002, California Primary Election. To register to vote, or to get
       additional information, visit the Vote America web site or call
                               1-800-345-VOTE.
                              Remember to Vote
    March 5, 2002, is the California Primary Election--remember to vote!
        Your vote is important. For your polling place location, call
                               1-800-345-VOTE.


